---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Card from "../components/Card.astro";
---

<Layout title="Welcome to TFYTFM">
	<main>
		<h1>Comming soon <span class="text-gradient">TFYTFM</span></h1>
		<section>
			<h2>Â¿What is it?</h2>
			<p>
				Today for You, Tomorrow for Me is a free software initiative
				that aims to empower youth without tech access, while also
				encouraging collaboration and service exchange among small
				businesses. Together, we're building an inclusive and equitable
				tech future.
			</p>
		</section>
		<section>
			<h2>Our Mission</h2>
			<p>
				Our mission is to provide access to software development
				education for children who would otherwise lack it. We believe
				in the power of education and technology to transform lives and
				opportunities.
			</p>
		</section>
		<section>
			<h2>Our Vision</h2>
			<p>
				Our vision is to create a software ecosystem and a community
				engaged in the development of free software. We want to promote
				service exchange among businesses and build a collaborative
				system where everyone can contribute and learn.
			</p>
		</section>
		<section>
			<h2>Why Today for You, Tomorrow for Me?</h2>
			<p>
				We believe in the principle of today for you, tomorrow for me,
				promoting a spirit of mutual help and collective growth. In our
				organization, every community member gets the chance to learn,
				grow, and help others do the same.
			</p>
		</section>

		<h3>Join Us</h3>
		<p>
			We invite you to join us in our mission. Whether you want to learn
			to code, contribute with your expertise in software development, or
			simply want to support our cause, there's a place for you in Today
			for You, Tomorrow for Me. Together, we can code a better future.
		</p>
		<a href="https://discord.com/invite/VTPH7rtZfg" class="button"
			>Join Discord</a
		>
	</main>
</Layout>

<style>
	main {
		padding: 2rem;
		max-width: var(--max-width);
		margin: 0 auto;
		color: white;
		font-size: 20px;
		line-height: 1.6;
	}

	h1 {
		font-size: 3rem;
		text-align: center;
		margin: 3rem 0;
		font-weight: 700;
	}

	section {
		background: rgba(var(--gray), 0.7);
		border-radius: 20px;
		padding: 2rem;
		margin: 2rem 0;
		transition: all 0.3s ease;
	}

	section:hover {
		transform: translateY(-5px);
		background: rgba(var(--accent), 0.1);
	}

	.text-gradient {
		background-image: var(--accent-gradient);
		-webkit-background-clip: text;
		-webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
		background-size: 400%;
		background-position: 0%;
	}

	/* BUTTON */
	.button {
		display: inline-block;
		padding: 10px 20px;
		font-size: 20px;
		text-align: center;
		text-decoration: none;
		background-color: #7289da;
		color: white;
		border-radius: 5px;
		transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
	}

	.button:hover {
		background-color: #5865f2;
	}
</style>
